data.value: Changelog: - Copmpletely rewritten - Improved GUI, modern style. - Improved loading times for startup, list loading, etc. - Improved search function - Added list creation by database - Added function to add staged pets (unfortunately with 0 durability) - Added bufffunction for pets - Added buttons for Soul Catalyst and other items - Added set creature value command - Added kill target command - Fixed huntaholic command ----------------------------------------------------------------------------- - Added Skills - Added red theme - Automatically removes the need for character if character has a color tag - Some bug fixes
